        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.boston.com/sports/baseball/redsox/gallery/07_04_2008_damon/">Boston Red Sox - Balance ball</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Bizarre event at today&#8217;s Sox/Yankees game. Johnny Damon caught a hit before colliding with the wall and losing the ball&#8230; which balanced atop the wall for a good second or two.  The photos are worth it for the gobsmacked Sox fan in the background.</p>

